description: Rodedawg International Industries, Inc. engages in manufacture and distribution of recreational, amphibious, and off road vehicles worldwide. It offers truck utility, sports utility, and convertible vehicles. The company was formerly known as E Jet Holdings, Inc. and changed its name to China Global Distribution Corporation. Later, the name was changed to Rodedawg International Industries, Inc. in 2005. Rodedawg International Industries is based in Sheridan, California.
